{"tid":1884950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭文貴：中共將於今年6月4日滅亡","createTime":"2020-02-18T03:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T18:54:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":177,"dislike":115,"uniUserReply":128,"replies":[{"pid":"86cc1828024ad96209dabb84bd83598a05f39f34","tid":1884950,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/18/phpkwmUEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F18%2FphpkwmUEi.jpg&h=81372548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（路透）<br />\n<br />\n流亡美國的中國富商郭文貴不定時暴露中國高層黑幕，15日在直播中又爆料，共產黨推行的中國夢已經完全不可能實現，今年6月4日「沒有共產黨的新中國一定會成立」，屆時會由世界上許多國家共同宣布。<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴表示，在武漢肺炎與美中貿易戰雙重影響下，「中國人在全世界的貿易信用和中國人的可信度和形象，在短時間內無法恢復」，且「決定中國經濟市場的經濟、技術、市場的美國，想在一定時間內恢復到以前，跟中國還像以前那樣做，幾乎不可能」，中國經濟只能是往生存型發展，「想當領導世界型發展那就是惡夢了，就不是中國夢了，別想了」。<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴爆料：「共產黨今年6月4號，不管是什麼情況下的滅，嘎嘣它走了或者被推翻了，甚至它還在那，都改變不了事實，6月4號宣布中華人民共和國沒有共產黨的新中國一定會成立，而且一定不僅僅是我說這話。記住，不僅僅是我宣布說這話，一定是世界上很多國家合法的權力會正式宣布。聽懂了嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴強調：「不僅是爆料革命宣布，很多國家合法機構會宣布，不在承認共產黨的合法執政地位，然後會推出中國人民的1人1票的、新的、有法治的這個中國政權。」<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴說：「我可以告訴大家，不管你接受不接受，就像幾個月以前你不接受這個疫情一樣，共產黨是沒了。是絕對沒了！現在就是中南坑那幾個傻貨，還在那塊蹦呢，跟當年的崇禎皇帝和慈禧都是1個德行的。死到臨頭他還不知道咋回事呢！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3071249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071249&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=b72a81fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071249&h=2b44cc57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3071249</a>"},{"pid":"e35aafdeefc46ca89a782ae3248922512b2ec25f","tid":1884950,"uid":155167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7828d1f5e7c890f5c93674e1c445afa0ca7af598","tid":1884950,"uid":85456,"like":280,"dislike":5,"score":275,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:06:28.000Z","msg":"范冰冰條片呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f957ab9e56b8884c765335e3ea36831c756d01ea","tid":1884950,"uid":51620,"like":117,"dislike":3,"score":114,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:07:06.000Z","msg":"犯冰冰含撚片"},{"pid":"66ba732255f34914ec9e4b63746b0060b4472b75","tid":1884950,"uid":175346,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:07:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b59d432dc8ac86eca6fd630a5a45c0d41ef1cd1","tid":1884950,"uid":121504,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:07:23.000Z","msg":"今年中共唔滅亡佢係咪要自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好唔捨得佢"},{"pid":"ef7aa47a40128ee1e31a52e85196592b507b0cee","tid":1884950,"uid":175346,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:08:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3890e313eafff2b1d85833e3b380f67c7946adb","tid":1884950,"uid":9962,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:09:26.000Z","msg":"佢嘅存在同大陸嘅希望工程一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddeb556d28c32c8dc89a1a168c0354405ae8f2a1","tid":1884950,"uid":60434,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:09:58.000Z","msg":"9upper"},{"pid":"def31a514e2033c550c450674aa489cffea2f21a","tid":1884950,"uid":86614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:10:19.000Z","msg":"又FF"},{"pid":"49f736a45b20debfe53cf34695e73d3bb99e05f3","tid":1884950,"uid":67340,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:10:24.000Z","msg":"唔係想否定佢反共嘅努力<br />\n但你成日鳩up冇樣中人地好難信你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片啊含撚片啊<i