/>\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2661924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2661924&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=9b5a9d0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2661924&h=4b21dc27\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2661924</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2019-01-04 16:32:40</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/12/06/4kDjBt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F12%2F06%2F4kDjBt.png&h=2d3a0463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n一直預告西方世界將與中國全面對抗的郭文貴還強調：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2020年是結束共產黨在中國的最後一年，否則文貴就從那18樓跳下去，大家要記住我的承諾。</strong></span>」"},{"pid":"1147551e3baa1b5e698c927f1d2876c2025c24a5","tid":1884950,"uid":245849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86cc1828024ad96209dabb84bd83598a05f39f34","tid":1884950,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/18/phpkwmUEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F18%2FphpkwmUEi.jpg&h=81372548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（路透）<br />\n<br />\n流亡美國的中國富商郭文貴不定時暴露中國高層黑幕，15日在直播中又爆料，共產黨推行的中國夢已經完全不可能實現，今年6月4日「沒有共產黨的新中國一定會成立」，屆時會由世界上許多國家共同宣布。<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴表示，在武漢肺炎與美中貿易戰雙重影響下，「中國人在全世界的貿易信用和中國人的可信度和形象，在短時間內無法恢復」，且「決定中國經濟市場的經濟、技術、市場的美國，想在一定時間內恢復到以前，跟中國還像以前那樣做，幾乎不可能」，中國經濟只能是往生存型發展，「想當領導世界型發展那就是惡夢了，就不是中國夢了，別想了」。<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴爆料：「共產黨今年6月4號，不管是什麼情況下的滅，嘎嘣它走了或者被推翻了，甚至它還在那，都改變不了事實，6月4號宣布中華人民共和國沒有共產黨的新中國一定會成立，而且一定不僅僅是我說這話。記住，不僅僅是我宣布說這話，一定是世界上很多國家合法的權力會正式宣布。聽懂了嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴強調：「不僅是爆料革命宣布，很多國家合法機構會宣布，不在承認共產黨的合法執政地位，然後會推出中國人民的1人1票的、新的、有法治的這個中國政權。」<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴說：「我可以告訴大家，不管你接受不接受，就像幾個月以前你不接受這個疫情一樣，共產黨是沒了。是絕對沒了！現在就是中南坑那幾個傻貨，還在那塊蹦呢，跟當年的崇禎皇帝和慈禧都是1個德行的。死到臨頭他還不知道咋回事呢！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3071249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071249&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=b72a81fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071249&h=2b44cc57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3071249</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:31:00.000Z","msg":"唔明白佢搞乜<br />\n睇來歷同背景唔似咁ON9嘅人<br />\n佢一直鳩吹個目的係咩？"},{"pid":"bddb057d4c0908aaa99fb53c34e889a80879605f","tid":1884950,"uid":67272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:31:01.000Z","msg":"文貴是否另類維穩工具?"},{"pid":"80cfa03ff2e84674eb145865d7d5fd115942f013","tid":1884950,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bddb057d4c0908aaa99fb53c34e889a80879605f","tid":1884950,"uid":67272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:31:01.000Z","msg":"文貴是否另類維穩工具?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:31:58.000Z","msg":"先唔好標籤<br />\n會唔會佢唔咁講就冇特殊保護？"},{"pid":"49cf054c95d454afb08304419ce1091723e91f3f","tid":1884950,"uid":227813,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:33:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢條撚樣你都信？</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9fd67d306ffda558ae821769bef0ab865b4cc2f7","tid":1884950,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:34:12.000Z","msg":"沒有共產黨<br />\n就沒有新中國"},{"pid":"379bf84ff26b7358a9b1a00b151855dc3eaa21c0","tid":1884950,"uid":127177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:34:55.000Z","msg":"個時間錦囊落得早左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"