like":280,"dislike":5,"score":275,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:06:28.000Z","msg":"范冰冰條片呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:52:18.000Z","msg":"X2"},{"pid":"6e94c253d6ac9a327ad07e59fc1165866d1ad165","tid":1884950,"uid":284192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:57:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VcQeg3bBk1I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVcQeg3bBk1I&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=f41c3292\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VcQeg3bBk1I</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>朱阿寶：「反抗暴政 推翻獨裁」，已經開響了革命第一槍 方斌起來了，我也站出來，希望更多人站起來。</strong>"},{"pid":"18321d103780c34d412055654a4171857823f40e","tid":1884950,"uid":162920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86cc1828024ad96209dabb84bd83598a05f39f34","tid":1884950,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/18/phpkwmUEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F18%2FphpkwmUEi.jpg&h=81372548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（路透）<br />\n<br />\n流亡美國的中國富商郭文貴不定時暴露中國高層黑幕，15日在直播中又爆料，共產黨推行的中國夢已經完全不可能實現，今年6月4日「沒有共產黨的新中國一定會成立」，屆時會由世界上許多國家共同宣布。<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴表示，在武漢肺炎與美中貿易戰雙重影響下，「中國人在全世界的貿易信用和中國人的可信度和形象，在短時間內無法恢復」，且「決定中國經濟市場的經濟、技術、市場的美國，想在一定時間內恢復到以前，跟中國還像以前那樣做，幾乎不可能」，中國經濟只能是往生存型發展，「想當領導世界型發展那就是惡夢了，就不是中國夢了，別想了」。<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴爆料：「共產黨今年6月4號，不管是什麼情況下的滅，嘎嘣它走了或者被推翻了，甚至它還在那，都改變不了事實，6月4號宣布中華人民共和國沒有共產黨的新中國一定會成立，而且一定不僅僅是我說這話。記住，不僅僅是我宣布說這話，一定是世界上很多國家合法的權力會正式宣布。聽懂了嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴強調：「不僅是爆料革命宣布，很多國家合法機構會宣布，不在承認共產黨的合法執政地位，然後會推出中國人民的1人1票的、新的、有法治的這個中國政權。」<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴說：「我可以告訴大家，不管你接受不接受，就像幾個月以前你不接受這個疫情一樣，共產黨是沒了。是絕對沒了！現在就是中南坑那幾個傻貨，還在那塊蹦呢，跟當年的崇禎皇帝和慈禧都是1個德行的。死到臨頭他還不知道咋回事呢！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3071249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071249&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=b72a81fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071249&h=2b44cc57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3071249</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:01:21.000Z","msg":"老實講我唔信 我係想支共滅 但我唔信咁短命"},{"pid":"393492e05b0b8cfb8c34aca08db2b281b0aa760f","tid":1884950,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:01:34.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢比中共更失實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片呢？"},{"pid":"d52044590088e41138269673955a24f10182d18c","tid":1884950,"uid":39383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:05:22.000Z","msg":"又係吹水佬"},{"pid":"f8c51f8178b42f4071c869624352af547af76fd0","tid":1884950,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇下點"},{"pid":"53fb7afb90c04c127565671ad9495a72304be3cd","tid":1884950,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:07:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1895894a1263f368ffe548e8cb2854426cf44db7","tid":1884950,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:09:23.000Z","msg":"一日睇唔到范冰冰扑野片一日我都唔會對佢講嘅野有任何評論"},{"pid":"0de93ead993f2cbf7daa03abfcbc70fce4c2edd2","tid":1884950,"uid":287494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:19:52.000Z","msg":"雖然條友吹很大，但難得有一大班中國人支持<br />\n唔想佢咁快穿煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e099cdca6fc18befbafc09495b53647c0ecbba59","tid":1884950,"uid":348712,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:25:16.00